t: Levolor - Wikipedia
s: March 18, 2025 - Levolor is an American manufacturer of custom window blinds and shades, as well as stock blinds and shades. Levolor is headquartered in the Atlanta, Georgia metropolitan area, and operates in the United States, Canada, Mexico, and China. The company was purchased by Hunter Douglas in 2016.
